opt = Optimizer([(-2.0, 2.0)], base_estimator=base_estimator, acq_func=
    acq_func, acq_optimizer='sampling', n_initial_points=2)
x1 = opt.ask()
opt.tell(x1, (bench1(x1), 1.0))
x2 = opt.ask()
res = opt.tell(x2, (bench1(x2), 2.0))
assert_true(x1 != x2)
assert_true(len(res.models) == 1)
assert_array_equal(res.func_vals.shape, (2,))
assert_array_equal(res.log_time.shape, (2,))
with pytest.raises(TypeError) as e:
    opt.tell(x2, bench1(x2))
pytest.mark.parametrize('base_estimator', TREE_REGRESSORS)pytest.mark.parametrize('acq_func', ACQ_FUNCS_PS)
